													<p itemprop="reviewBody">We love Victorinox ! Great price and quality. Best prices! Webstaurant store is so convenient to shop. We love this product. Get it for your kitchen if you need a knife. </p>

														<ul class="rating" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="http://Schema.org/Rating">
															<meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5">

																<li class="icon-star"></li>
															
														</ul>
													 
													<div class="clears"></div>
													<p itemprop="reviewBody">Our chefs love this knife.  Comes in very sharp and has great weight and balance.  The handle has a great grip and cleans up very easily.  Great all around knife and easy to sharpen.  </p>

										<li class="media" itemprop="review" itemscope itemtype="http://Schema.org/Review">
											<div class="media-body box padded" id="review_269359">
												
												
														<ul class="rating" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="http://Schema.org/Rating">
															<meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5">
															<input type="hidden" id="numHelpful" value="0">

																<li class="icon-star"></li>
															
																<li class="icon-star"></li>
															
																<li class="icon-star"></li>
															
																<li class="icon-star"></li>
															
																<li class="icon-star"></li>
															
														</ul>
													 
													<div class="clears"></div>
													<p itemprop="reviewBody">I bought two of these on the recommendation in Cooks Illustrated for use in my food truck.  Its a great work horse knife that holds an edge quite well.  Handle feels nice in the hand as well. </p>
													<p class="header-4">
														<strong itemprop="author">Dan B.</strong>

													</p>

										</li>

														<ul class="rating" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="http://Schema.org/Rating">
															<meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5">
															<input type="hidden" id="numHelpful" value="0">

																<li class="icon-star"></li>
															
																<li class="icon-star"></li>
															
																<li class="icon-star"></li>
															
																<li class="icon-star"></li>
															
																<li class="icon-star"></li>
															
														</ul>
													 
													<div class="clears"></div>
													<p itemprop="reviewBody">Bought this knife at the recommendation of a gentleman that sharpens knifes for a living. I do not regret it at all, great quality and balance.</p>
													<p class="header-4">
														<strong itemprop="author">Mark T.</strong>
														
															<span class="small">Posted on <span itemprop="datePublished">04/14/2015</span></span>
														
													</p>

										</li>

														<ul class="rating" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="http://Schema.org/Rating">
															<meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5">
															<input type="hidden" id="numHelpful" value="0">
															<input type="hidden" id="ratingDate" value="2014-10-09">
															
																<li class="icon-star"></li>
															
																<li class="icon-star"></li>
															
																<li class="icon-star"></li>
															
																<li class="icon-star"></li>
															
																<li class="icon-star"></li>
															
														</ul>
													 
													<div class="clears"></div>
													<p itemprop="reviewBody">this 12" chef knife is a very high quality product. the edge is super strong and long lasting. the design makes it really easy to clean. and this price is great.</p>
													<p class="header-4">
														<strong itemprop="author">elizabeth H.</strong>
														
															<span class="small">Posted on <span itemprop="datePublished">10/09/2014</span></span>
														
													</p>
												
											</div>
											
											
										</li>

														<ul class="rating" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="http://Schema.org/Rating">
															<meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5">
															<input type="hidden" id="numHelpful" value="0">
															<input type="hidden" id="ratingDate" value="2014-01-25">
															
																<li class="icon-star"></li>
															
																<li class="icon-star"></li>
															
																<li class="icon-star"></li>
															
																<li class="icon-star"></li>
															
																<li class="icon-star"></li>
															
														</ul>
													 
													<div class="clears"></div>
													<p itemprop="reviewBody">This is the only chef knife I use on a daily bases for three reasons. It holds an edge well. It is one of the easiest knifes to sharpen. lastly it's very affordable. This knife is an all round great addition to anyone's kitchen.  </p>
													<p class="header-4">
														<strong itemprop="author">Matthew T.</strong>
														
															<span class="small">Posted on <span itemprop="datePublished">01/25/2014</span></span>
														
													</p>
												
											</div>
											
											
										</li>
										

										<li class="media" itemprop="review" itemscope itemtype="http://Schema.org/Review">
											<div class="media-body box padded" id="review_6428">
												
												
														<ul class="rating" itemprop="reviewRating" itemscope itemtype="http://Schema.org/Rating">
															<meta itemprop="ratingValue" content="5">
															<input type="hidden" id="numHelpful" value="0">
															<input type="hidden" id="ratingDate" value="2010-06-25">
															
																<li class="icon-star"></li>
															
																<li class="icon-star"></li>
															
																<li class="icon-star"></li>
															
																<li class="icon-star"></li>
															
																<li class="icon-star"></li>
															
														</ul>
													 
													<div class="clears"></div>
													<p itemprop="reviewBody">This is one of the best knives for the money that I have used.  I have had 2 for at least ten years, using one commercially and one at home. Be advised, this is a BIG knife.  I am a big guy, so it really fits me ergonomically, but those not needing that length may find it a little slow.  I find that my 8 1/2" Forschner Chef Knife is much easier to manage for those under 6' tall.  Fibrox handle is easy to keep clean and fits my hand well.</p>
													<p class="header-4">
														<strong itemprop="author">David K.</strong>
														
															<span class="small">Posted on <span itemprop="datePublished">06/25/2010</span></span>
														
													</p>
